name: NOBLE EDUCATIONAL EMPOWERMENT SOCIETY
briefDescription: Organization Profile:  Noble educational empowerment society (NEES) was founded in the year 2005. It started small project in Ranga Reddy district of Andhra Pradesh. NEES focus was educational empowerment. The project “Udaan” was conceptualized to build capacities of the rural youth by providing industry and trade specific skill development programs to build the gap between Industry requirement and market availability.However in 2009 the organization shifted its priorities from mere skill development program to a larger growth of the poor communities.
